Mimic-3
- Starts the game with no powers. Upon the permanent death of a non-royalty team member, the mimic gets the role of the dead teammate. 
- Once during the game, can choose to copy any player's role, to gain the role for 2 nights. Choosing a royalty role or a solo role will return a warrior role.
- All other restrictions and conditions are inherited from the acquired role.
- Role conversion is instant. Copying is instant.
- Respawns in 2 phases as the mimic, and then takes the respawn time of the acquired role.
